{"title":"西财摄记｜忽而今夏","uid":"7269716cb17cff2efbecc9bd1aa4ae5a","slug":"推文4","date":"2021-06-09T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-03T15:39:52.876Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/推文4.json","keywords":null,"cover":"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224942697.png","content":"<p><strong>小夏引微凉，悠悠夏日长。我们在夏枝繁茂时再见。</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224742834.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224742834\"></p>\n<p>立夏过去了，天气渐热，不知不觉就进入了夏天</p>\n<h2 id=\"小裙子是夏天的入场券\"><a href=\"#小裙子是夏天的入场券\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"小裙子是夏天的入场券\"></a>小裙子是夏天的入场券</h2><p><em>“ 连雨不知春去，一晴方觉夏深 ”</em></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224814043.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224814043\"></p>\n<p>都的初夏再美好不过了，日落变晚，白昼拉长；</p>\n<p>气温还没有太炎热，却也足够穿上喜欢的小裙子。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224839497.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224839497\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224844793.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224844793\"></p>\n<p>JK，青春的象征</p>\n<p>好像所有关于青春的故事，也都发生在夏天</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224854659.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224854659\"></p>\n<p>校医院后的树林也变得繁茂，</p>\n<p>远远望去，像一片小森林，清凉又惬意；</p>\n<p>选择在这里拍摄一组青春感的JK夏日写真再合适。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224912594.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224912594\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"悠悠夏日长\"><a href=\"#悠悠夏日长\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"悠悠夏日长\"></a>悠悠夏日长</h2><p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224925482.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224925482\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224931453.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224931453\"></p>\n<p>拍摄当天，小糖散着头发，</p>\n<p>穿着一身经典款的水手服，奔向我，</p>\n<p>我便知道了我想要的感觉，</p>\n<p>没有好天气，那就打灯吧～<img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224942697.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224942697\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"忽而今夏\"><a href=\"#忽而今夏\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"忽而今夏\"></a>忽而今夏</h2><p>从南门大草坪到人品园附近的道路，</p>\n<p>奔跑着向下的时候，</p>\n<p>感觉夏天的风已经吹拂在耳边了</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303224959993.png\" alt=\"image-20220303224959993\"></p>\n<p>看着提着制服包的小糖，漫步在草坪上，</p>\n<p>回头冲我一笑，</p>\n<p>快门咔嚓，记录下了这一刻</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225050391.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225050391\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225055592.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225055592\"></p>\n<p>表情动作的引导，没有太刻意的摆拍，</p>\n<p>更希望呈现出少女漫步校园的悠闲感与青春感</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225105137.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225105137\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225110452.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225110452\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225118312.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225118312\"></p>\n<p>谁说只有春天的花儿美呢？</p>\n<p>夏天的绿意也很令人愉快~</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://deels-photos.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/uPic/image-20220303225126760.png\" alt=\"image-20220303225126760\"></p>\n<p>趁着青春正好，记录下这清澈的岁月时光吧</p>\n<p> 下期再会啦</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>感谢</summary>\n<p>文|李宜霏</p>\n<p>摄|刘雨童</p>\n<p>出镜|唐知宇</p>\n<p>排版|张玥</p>\n\n</details>\n","text":"小夏引微凉，悠悠夏日长。我们在夏枝繁茂时再见。 立夏过去了，天气渐热，不知不觉就进入了夏天 小裙子是夏天的入场券“ 连雨不知春去，一晴方觉夏深 ” 都的初夏再美好不过了，日落变晚，白昼拉长； 气温还没有太炎热，却也足够穿上喜欢的小裙子。 JK，青春的象征 好像所有关于青春的故事，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":490,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"西财摄记","slug":"西财摄记","count":4,"path":"api/categories/西财摄记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"夏","slug":"夏","count":6,"path":"api/tags/夏.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\